    "body": "@tommoor You can't create that type of window in Electron can you? All windows are the standard windows. To create that style, you would need to build it yourself in HTML/CSS as far as I know.\n\nSo because of that I'm not sure how the fade effect would be enabled at the OS level... unless that type of window was added to the browser window API as an option? In any case you could animate a standard window that has been styled up to look the same by listening to the focus and blur events and then animating the window contents. And then create your own animations, etc.\n"
  },
