    "created_at": "2015-11-03T07:52:37Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-03T07:52:46Z",
    "body": "> definitely something that belongs at an OS level :smile:\n\nI would also really appreciate a native fadeIn and fadeOut method on BrowserWindows, where the OS supports it.\n\nWe recently switched to using a BrowserWindow instead of a Tray menu because the current implementation of the Tray menu prevents item labels from being updated while the menu is visible, and resetting the menu causes the menu to close.\n"
  },
