    "created_at": "2015-11-16T20:03:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-16T20:03:46Z",
    "body": "Hey folks–I think this is a great idea. Would love to be able to fade windows in and out, especially on Mac OS X. In N1 we've also been transitioning window size by calling setBounds over and over again. \n\nI'd like to propose an API allowing for animated changes to both opacity and size—something like this.\n\n```\nbrowserWindow.transition(function() {\n   browserWindow.setOpacity(0);\n}, 200);\n```\n\nThoughts?\n"
  },
