    "updated_at": "2016-10-13T18:13:28Z",
    "body": "Here is probably the most performant code for Windows with [AnimateWindow](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/desktop/ms632669%28v=vs.85%29.aspx)\n\nFades in 1000ms and out 1000ms\n\n```\n    let Animatro = ffi.Library(\"User32.dll\", {\n        'AnimateWindow' : ['bool', ['int','int','int']]\n    })\n    let handle = mainWindow.getNativeWindowHandle().readInt32LE(0);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n        Animatro.AnimateWindow(handle, 1000, 589824); // 0x00080000 | 0x00010000 (hide the window, blend + hide)\n    }, 3000);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n        Animatro.AnimateWindow(handle, 1000, 524288); // 0x00080000 shows the window (blend only)\n    }, 6000);\n```\n"
  },
